casebody.data:
Before Fitzsimons, Ch. J., and O’Dwyer, J.

Isaac Dubinsky, Respondent, v. The Metropolitan Wrapper Company, Appellant. Appeal from a judgment upon a verdict in favor of the plaintiff, directed by the court, and from an order denying a motion for a new trial. Archibald C. Shenstone, for appellant; Henry Kuntz, for respondent. Judgment and oraer appealed from affirmed, with costs.

No opinion.
